{"id": "1410909473178124379", "channel_id": "1410909473178124379", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "烈日坠入大海，海滩上的欢腾声戛然而止——\n水汽蒸腾间一道金黄的身影隐现，竟有点像一只刚出炉还冒着热气的“烤地瓜”。\n“吵醒我睡觉的人，必须付出代价”，冷冽的枪口抵住守密人额头！这场海滩危机该如何化解？\n\n🏝️特别活动「黑阳垂照的永夏」，将于9 月 1 日 9:00 - 9 月 15 日 9:00 开启！\n🏝️为大家奉上活动奖励预览图：\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nThe scorching sun plunges beneath the waves, and the cheerful din of the beach ceases as if severed by a knife.\nThrough the shimmering veil of rising steam, a figure emerges, forged of gilded light. \nA cold gun barrel presses into your forehead. \n“Whoever dares to wake me,” she whispers, “let’s just say that’s a bill that comes due immediately.”\nOh no. How do you resolve this beachside crisis?\n\n🏝️Special event \"Summer under Black Sun\" will be available from <t:1756688400:F> to <t:1757898000:F>\n🏝️Check out the Event Rewards below:", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T08:50:31.836000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "🇧🇷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1410909474130235452", "filename": "-0829.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 5219184, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1410909473178124379/1410909474130235452/-0829.jpg?ex=69ccdc58&is=69cb8ad8&hm=494eaaf467b10085fa9df6edfbf7b474751cee8bcd6b061701cf51883e9e09a6&"}, {"id": "1410909475052716103", "filename": "-0829.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 5319383, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1410909473178124379/1410909475052716103/-0829.jpg?ex=69ccdc58&is=69cb8ad8&hm=5d9c9e89df8f59b65caaa2f7813f23c152a58d928266d2969bb12a84ca97cd92&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1410909473178124379", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特别活动「黑阳垂照的永夏」，奖励一览！Summer under Black Sun: Rewards Overview!",