{"id": "1411036979172212818", "channel_id": "1410909473178124379", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@264894122148495362> <@290209576366637056> <@618475034465533954> We’ve received your feedback! This originated from the Japanese version’s launch content, and we’ll do our best to ensure the global version also has a chance to obtain it. How to share content between the global and Japanese versions is a major challenge for us.\nFor the regular gacha and character-associated Wheels, we’ll continue with the previous printmaking art style. However, special Wheels originating from the Japanese version will experiment with a different illustration style—similar to the special approach we used for Ramonna’s Valentine’s commemorative Wheel.", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T17:17:11.634000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-29T17:31:01.595000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["290209576366637056", "264894122148495362", "618475034465533954"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Emoji_LT_R_02", "emoji_id": "1400771683664658433", "count": 7}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1410909473178124379", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特别活动「黑阳垂照的永夏」，奖励一览！Summer under Black Sun: Rewards Overview!", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363"}
{"id": "1411037065738715291", "channel_id": "1410909473178124379", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我们收到了你们的反馈！这是源于日本版的开服内容，我们会尽力确保国际版也有机会获取。如何共享国际版和日本版的游戏内容是我们一大挑战。游戏的常规抽卡、角色对应的命轮都会坚持以前的版画艺术风格，但是源于日本版的特殊命轮会尝试跟之前拉蒙娜情人节纪念命轮类似采用特殊的插画风格。", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T17:17:32.273000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1410909473178124379", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特别活动「黑阳垂照的永夏」，奖励一览！Summer under Black Sun: Rewards Overview!", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363"}
