{"id": "1411039811627778048", "channel_id": "1405526119628935230", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@1154601435141509192> <@88644018673582080> <@244028747999608832> <@195401302145105920> Thank you for your feedback! We will try to provide advance notices whenever possible, but as we’ve had repeated delays in the past, it’s still quite challenging on the execution side right now. Also, similar to new character reveals, we’d like to keep a bit of mystery and anticipation, so we won’t announce too much too early. Our goal is to give everyone about one month of lead time to plan and prepare.\nOn the other hand, once the triple reruns begin, the interval before a unit’s next rerun won’t be as long as it used to be.", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T17:28:26.944000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["88644018673582080", "195401302145105920", "1154601435141509192", "244028747999608832"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "celestepray", "emoji_id": "1397414070100951110", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405526119628935230", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜V2.3.1 版本前瞻┊ Version Outlook", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
